01:16:41.359 --> 01:16:42.698
Who is it?

546
01:16:42.897 --> 01:16:44.059
Paul.

547
01:16:47.699 --> 01:16:49.091
Hang on.

548
01:17:27.146 --> 01:17:29.368
It's going to be here
soon or later.

549
01:17:32.504 --> 01:17:34.482
You could
pass it on.

550
01:17:37.043 --> 01:17:38.580
You did once.

551
01:17:39.029 --> 01:17:40.451
Shouldn't have.

552
01:17:42.466 --> 01:17:43.943
I could.

553
01:17:45.184 --> 01:17:46.297
No.

554
01:17:47.881 --> 01:17:49.942
I like you too.
You know.

555
01:17:52.850 --> 01:17:54.716
Why you picked Greg?

556
01:17:55.857 --> 01:17:58.055
I thought he'll be okay.

557
01:18:01.560 --> 01:18:03.537
He wasn't scared.

558
01:18:06.889 --> 01:18:09.842
He said to go to high school
wasn't a bigh deal.

559
01:18:38.178 --> 01:18:40.208
I want to help.

560
01:18:40.621 --> 01:18:42.283
Do you?

561
01:18:43.552 --> 01:18:45.667
Yeah.
I do .

562
01:19:16.624 --> 01:19:17.911
Jay?

563
01:19:18.323 --> 01:19:19.578
Yeah?

564
01:19:20.692 --> 01:19:22.424
Do you trust me?

565
01:19:26.175 --> 01:19:29.728
Do you remember where we were.
The first time we kissed.

566
01:19:46.102 --> 01:19:47.273
You know where to go?

567
01:19:47.298 --> 01:19:49.505
I know how to go
there. you'll see.

568
01:19:52.022 --> 01:19:54.549
I haven't been to the pool
since I was 14.

569
01:19:55.136 --> 01:19:57.247
Who brought you there?

570
01:19:57.964 --> 01:19:58.993
Okay.

571
01:19:59.235 --> 01:20:02.954
That's where I had my first beer.
I threw up the whole night.

572
01:20:02.994 --> 01:20:05.978
- Into the pool?
- No. outside the car.

573
01:20:05.978 --> 01:20:07.318
And in the car.

574
01:20:07.827 --> 01:20:09.182
Paul used to pee in it.

575
01:20:09.207 --> 01:20:10.753
Eww.
Disgusting.

576
01:20:10.778 --> 01:20:13.264
Whatever.
There's chlorine.

577
01:20:58.510 --> 01:21:00.385
When I was a little girl.

578
01:21:00.655 --> 01:21:03.366
my parents wouldn't allow me
to go south of 8 Mile.

579
01:21:04.435 --> 01:21:07.331
And I didn't even know what that meant
until I got a little older.

580
01:21:07.457 --> 01:21:09.705
And I started realizing that

581
01:21:09.741 --> 01:21:12.722
that's where the city started
and the suburbs ended.

582
01:21:13.641 --> 01:21:17.082
And I used to think about
how shitty and weird that was.

583
01:21:17.623 --> 01:21:18.491
I mean.

584
01:21:18.523 --> 01:21:23.694
I had to ask permission to go to the state fair
with my best friend and her parents.

585
01:21:23.977 --> 01:21:27.287
Only because it was
a few blocks past the border.

586
01:21:27.517 --> 01:21:29.705
My mom said the same thing.

587
01:22:22.714 --> 01:22:24.730
How long do you think it'll be?

588
01:22:27.939 --> 01:22:29.439
I don't know.

589
01:22:30.020 --> 01:22:31.894
Are you always that bad.

590
01:26:26.282 --> 01:26:27.921
Oh my God.

591
01:26:29.145 --> 01:26:31.167
It just walked into the room.
It's right there.

592
01:26:31.192 --> 01:26:32.404
It's here?

593
01:26:32.754 --> 01:26:33.912
Right there!

594
01:26:34.317 --> 01:26:36.936
Jay. what do you see?

595
01:26:37.792 --> 01:26:39.784
I don't want to tell you.

596
01:26:40.049 --> 01:26:42.401
Jay. I need you to
point at it. okay?

597
01:26:42.485 --> 01:26:45.157
Keep your finger aim at it
so we can see where it is.

598
01:26:49.717 --> 01:26:51.805
Is it getting in the water?

599
01:26:53.943 --> 01:26:56.652
It's just standing there.
staring at me.

600
01:26:57.647 --> 01:26:59.070
It's moving.

601
01:26:59.114 --> 01:27:00.523
What's it doing?

602
01:27:00.548 --> 01:27:02.409
It's walking!
It's just walking!

603
01:27:03.702 --> 01:27:06.242
- Paul. I want to get out!
- No! Just wait for it to get in!

604
01:27:06.267 --> 01:27:08.400
No. I don't want to do this.
I just want to get out!

605
01:27:08.425 --> 01:27:09.957
- What the fuck?
- Jay!

606
01:27:09.982 --> 01:27:11.241
Out out of there!

607
01:27:12.079 --> 01:27:14.016
She's gonna get electrocuted!

608
01:27:14.218 --> 01:27:15.675
No. it didn't work.

609
01:27:15.700 --> 01:27:17.403
- You okay?!?
- Yeah.

610
01:27:17.428 --> 01:27:19.548
- Didn't work.
- Thank god!

611
01:27:22.433 --> 01:27:24.021
Jay. look out!

612
01:27:24.972 --> 01:27:27.758
- Oh my god. somebody help her!
- What do we do?!?

613
01:27:44.317 --> 01:27:46.394
What the hell is going on?!?

614
01:28:02.278 --> 01:28:04.222
Jay. just keep pointing at it!

615
01:28:11.423 --> 01:28:13.118
It's right there!

616
01:28:16.059 --> 01:28:17.541
Where is it?!?

617
01:28:19.344 --> 01:28:21.060
Watch out.
don't get too close!

618
01:28:21.154 --> 01:28:22.850
It's right there!

619
01:28:24.963 --> 01:28:26.525
Yara!

620
01:28:34.432 --> 01:28:35.652
Where?

621
01:28:36.176 --> 01:28:37.297
Here?

622
01:28:38.478 --> 01:28:40.004
- Here?
- Right there!

623
01:28:50.280 --> 01:28:51.543
Where is it?

624
01:29:04.067 --> 01:29:06.160
- Jay!
- Come on. Jay!

625
01:29:08.075 --> 01:29:10.296
- Give me your hand!
- Come on. come on. come on!

626
01:29:12.289 --> 01:29:13.433
Jay!

627
01:30:00.583 --> 01:30:01.877
Jay?

628
01:30:03.209 --> 01:30:04.688
Do you see it?

629
01:30:04.713 --> 01:30:06.554
Is it still down there?

630
01:32:43.450 --> 01:32:45.792
Do you feel any different?

631
01:33:01.919 --> 01:33:03.587
Do you?

632
01:33:09.711 --> 01:33:10.985
No.

633
01:34:05.119 --> 01:34:08.579
<i>"When there is torture. there is pain and wounds.</i>

634
01:34:08.604 --> 01:34:13.738
<i>physical agony. and all this
distracts the mind from mental suffering.</i>

635
01:34:13.836 --> 01:34:18.706
<i>so that one is tormented only by
the wounds until the moment of death.</i>

636
01:34:20.452 --> 01:34:25.228
<i>And the most terrible agony may not be
in the wounds themselves</i>

637
01:34:25.374 --> 01:34:29.074
<i>but in knowing for certain that within an hour.</i>

638
01:34:29.449 --> 01:34:33.674
<i>then within ten minutes. then within half a minute.</i>

639
01:34:33.896 --> 01:34:37.133
<i>then now. at this very instant –</i>

640
01:34:37.423 --> 01:34:39.442
<i>your soul will leave your body</i>

641
01:34:39.543 --> 01:34:42.472
<i>and you will no longer be a person.</i>

642
01:34:43.160 --> 01:34:45.163
<i>and that this is certain;</i>

643
01:34:45.341 --> 01:34:49.969
<i>the worst thing is that it is certain.”</i>

643
01:34:50.305 --> 01:35:50.252
